name: Objektivis Lens Cap - f/22
description:
F/22 refers to the small f-stop (aperture) for strong depth of focus. If you like that sharpness, then that’s your lens cap!

Front protection lens cap made of plastic material in black base-color. Side pinch for easy clipping the cap on your camera lens. UV-print, lightly structured surface.

Fits for all camera lenses with the diameter filter mentioned in the size-dropdown below.
